---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Contact — Lance Owide"
  description="Get in touch with Lance Owide."
>
  <div class="page">
    <div class="page-header">
      <div class="page-label">Contact</div>
      <h1 class="page-title">Get in touch</h1>
      <p class="page-desc">Open to interesting conversations about B2B commerce, AI, and new opportunities.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-grid">
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/lance-owide/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="card contact-card">
        <div class="contact-icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-body">
          <div class="contact-label">LinkedIn</div>
          <div class="contact-value">linkedin.com/in/lance-owide</div>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-arrow">→</div>
      </a>

      <a href="https://mentorcruise.com/mentor/lanceowide/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="card contact-card">
        <div class="contact-icon mentor-icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-body">
          <div class="contact-label">Mentoring</div>
          <div class="contact-value">Available on MentorCruise</div>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-arrow">→</div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-note">
      <p>
        I'm particularly open to conversations about <strong>B2B commerce strategy</strong>,
        <strong>AI applications in business</strong>, and <strong>go-to-market for SaaS</strong>.
        If you're building something interesting, reach out.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .contact-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .contact-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .contact-icon {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .mentor-icon {
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
    border-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
    color: #10b981;
  }

  .contact-body {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .contact-label {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-subtle);
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }

  .contact-value {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .contact-arrow {
    color: var(--text-subtle);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    transition: color 0.15s, transform 0.15s;
  }

  .contact-card:hover .contact-arrow {
    color: var(--accent);
    transform: translateX(3px);
  }

  .contact-note {
    max-width: 560px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }

  .contact-note p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .contact-note strong {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
</style>
